title: Sins Of The Fallen v1 1-4 - The Nightstalker (2005) (g-seti-OCD)
description:
English | CBR | 4 Issues

Sins Of The Fallen v1 #1-4 - The Nightstalker
Publisher:  Zenescope
Publication Date:  November 30, 2005 - April 12, 2006

Writer:  Ralph Tedesco and Joe Tyler
Penciler and Inker:  H.G. Young
Colorist:  Transparency Digital
Letterer:  Dave Lanphear
Cover:  David Seidman

"The Nightstalker" begins in present day Philadelphia where a serial killer is leaving behind a gruesome trail of dismembered victims. Ted Banks, a young hot-shot journalist with a knack for digging up the truth, is assigned to cover the story. But his instinct tells him there's more to these murders than what meets the eye and he's determined to find out what exactly it is.

The series was cancelled before issue #5 was released.

Thanks goes to g-seti for this release.
